Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.23,0:02:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Storm's cleared up for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to leave by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a good\Nfeeling about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you okay?\N- (scoffs) Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wake you guys up just before sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.73,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,(liquid swishes)\N(gulping)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,(Qrow sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,(fire crackling)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Oscar] It's a diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- The head of this household, Bartleby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he and several other families
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,founded this little settlement\Nto try and live on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it worked,\Nat least for a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Grimm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just one of many hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowed down their farming,\Nmade everything harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed like quite the ambitious fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Always thinking of new\Nschemes to overcome the odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Qrow said we should get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna head out early tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- The last thing you'll catch me doing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is letting some kid tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go to bed!" (scoffs)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,(bottle clatters)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,(screams)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Close the window!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uncle Qrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- (groans) Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Ruby] We overslept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,(groans)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(bottle shatters)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- (groans) What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- You know, you can\Ntalk to me about stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yang, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's just get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Weiss] There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can we just go back to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- If we're all so tired, maybe\Nwe should make breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- You wanna make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,(trailer clatters)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- You guys got the bike ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, it's done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's hook this thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(tires hissing)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,(groans)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- You people are just beacons\Nfor bad luck, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm starting to think the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,just doesn't want us getting to Atlas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's just a flat tire,\NI'm sure there's a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's not just that, it's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Storms, crashes, monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're always\Nhaving to fight to get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's what we signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- We signed up to try and save the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,not just delay the inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Last night I,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.12,0:06:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we even going to Atlas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Weiss, we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozpin hid the relics behind giant doors
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,under enormous schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But how long would it\Ntake Salem to find a lamp
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grimm might--\N- They'd find it eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.53,0:07:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,sure, but bury it or just\Nthrow it down the well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,it would take years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It might not even happen in our lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But we could be done with it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,(snow crunches)\N- I am really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(sighs)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)\N(Ruby screams)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby, it's okay.\N- No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's something down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it, it was looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go.\N- What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave, we\Nhave to go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get the lamp back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Qrow] All we have to\Ndo is fix this trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, farm boy, check the shed for a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm not leaving without the lamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- (sighs) I'll go down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll go down together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the stupid lamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar, fix the stupid tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,(water splashing)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Maybe the current carried it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, come on, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- Turn off your lights and\Njust look for the glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- There.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(water splashing)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guys, I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,(screaming)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ruby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,(weapon firing)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,(Grimm groan)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- My weapon feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.54,0:12:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,(groaning)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- An exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,An exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Blake,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,(Grimm hissing)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- I've got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(doors clatter)\N- They're locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(groaning)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- [Maria] Ruby,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what color are your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- They're silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- You have a family, friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't think about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about the people who love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus on the thought of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the way they make you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.17,0:14:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.00,0:14:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it must
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,(Grimm shrieks)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're back in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uncle Qrow, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- We're leaving, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,(bottles shattering)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:15:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,(flames crackling)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now we can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop it, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,(dramatic instrumental music)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(engines revving)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,(flames crackling)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not strong or ferocious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They drain your will to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartleby's estate was hemorrhaging\Nmoney towards the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to cut costs\Non Huntsman protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But in order to do that\Nhe needed everyone calm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,always.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Managed to get two away from their pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hike back was miserable, but\Ngot the bastards in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wife thinks I was out sealing\Nthe waterway entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it tomorrow and tell her the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,once these things take\Nthe edge off of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- The next page proves that he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but not before the rest of the pack
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,followed their missing\Npair all the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My guess is they made their\Nway beneath the estate
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,through the water tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That Bartleby sealed up the next morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartleby's plan worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was angry or sad or scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then no one was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm sorry for what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,about giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't quit until the lamp is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It was those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The signs were all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd never seen an entire settlement
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,withered away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose my mind just\Nisn't what it used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Miss Calavera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know so much about the Grimm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the tunnels you\Nknew exactly what to say
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to make me... to make my eyes do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, isn't it obvious, girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I had silver eyes.
